                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; names of the donors; the word salām;
                           incipits of the text and its subsections (a few lines are rubricated,
                           alternating with black lines, at the beginning of the commemorative
                           notices for each month: fols. 5r, 35v, 59v, 89v, 117v, 155r,
                           180rb-180rc); parts of names in Additio 1; elements of punctuation signs;
                           elements of the quire marks (fols. 15r, 25r, 35r, 45r, 55r, 65r, 85r,
                           115r, 125r, 135r, 145r, 175r); elements of Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
                     </handNote>
