               <provenance>Walatta Madḫǝn is mentioned in the
                     supplication formulas throughout the Ms., as well as other members of her
                     family: Walda Krǝstos (e.g., 32vb, 58va, 94rb,
                     103va), Gabra Māryām (12rb, 55rc), Walatta Māryām
                        (13rb, 53rc, 93ra, 129vc), Wǝddāse Māryām
                        (24vc, 48rc, 93vb, 138rb), Gabra Yoḥannǝs
                        (25rb, 44va, 95vb, 152rc).
 All names are
                     added by a recent hand (same as that of Additiones 1, 2, 3) in deep vermilion
                     ink. The church of ʾabuna Libānos (probably of Mäsṭǝḥ) is mention as the owner of
                     the Ms. in Additiones 1, 3.</provenance></history>
